- Rule: **Audit workflow** in `.cursor/rules/feature-thread-workflow.mdc` (**auto-starts** on audit / quality / LOC / optimize-scope requests)
- Packs: `.cursor/feature-prompts/audit-<scope>/` with `packType: audit` in README
