- Checklist: **Audit checklist** in `frontend-engineering-partner.mdc` (layering, duplication, dead code; no app diffs in audit phases)
- After audit: implementation via separate `feature-*` packs referencing finding IDs
- **Second validation round:** mandatory pass; diff stats - `frontend-engineering-partner.mdc`
- **Rules evolution:** repeatable gaps â†’ update `.cursor/rules/` in same session - **Rules evolution** in `frontend-engineering-partner.mdc`
- **Search-first / no boilerplate:** see **Search-first, minimal code, no duplication** in `frontend-engineering-partner.mdc`
- **File size >500 lines:** split/refactor only when pertinent (cohesive long files are OK) - see `frontend-engineering-partner.mdc` â†’ **File size (>500 lines)**
