## Git workflow

- Rule: **Git Workflow (human gate)** in `frontend-engineering-partner.mdc`
- No automatic push or commit
- **Build gate (blocking):** run `npm run build` and get `Build: pass` in the session before any `git commit` or `git push` on application code; fix failures first
- End of implementation: stage with selective `git add`, propose commit message + breakdown; user validates before commit/push
- **Feature-scoped commits:** when ~8+ files or 2+ domains - split into one commit per feature/domain; sequential commits on user request; never default to one monolithic commit

