`react`, `react-dom`, `zeos-link`, `@caterpillar-labs/zeos-zfilesystem`, `@wharfkit/antelope`, `vite`, `typescript`

## Directory layout

```
src/
  main.tsx              React entry
  App.tsx               Demo UI and page state
  config.ts             Env-backed config
  styles.css            Global styles
  components/           Reusable UI (render only)
  components/dropdown/  Dropdown.tsx (searchable Cloak select)
  types/dropdownTypes.ts
  constants/connectedInputGroupConstants.ts
  providers/            React context (ChainMetadataProvider, LanguageProvider)
  lib/                  Business logic (no React)
    chainApi.ts         Defibox table reads
    chainMetadata.ts    Alias networks/tokens + zfilesystem icon decode
    defibox.ts          Pair parsing, BigInt quotes
    eosioAsset.ts       Asset helpers
    balances.ts         CLOAK balance parsing
    zeos.ts             Wallet connect + swap zactions
    tokenIcon.ts        Fallback colors + static icon paths
```

## Architecture rules

- **`src/lib/`** - chain reads, Defibox math, zeos-link; no React
- **`src/components/`** - render only
- **`src/App.tsx`** - orchestration; extract hooks when logic grows
- Prefer **`src/hooks/`** and **`src/types/`** only when the demo outgrows a single page file

## Blockchain integration

### CLOAK-only wallet

- Connect via `zeos-link` / ZEOS Link WebSocket (`VITE_ZEOS_LINK_URL`)
- Swap: `spend` + `mint` zactions built in `src/lib/zeos.ts`
- **No** Anchor / TokenPocket / WharfKit in this repo

### Defibox direct swap

- Contract: `swap.defi` (env: `VITE_SWAP_CONTRACT`)
- Tables: `config`, `pairs`
- Memo: `swap,<min_out_units>,<pair_id>` - direct pair only, no routing
- **BigInt-only** asset math in `src/lib/defibox.ts` and `src/lib/eosioAsset.ts`
- CLOAK `mint` must use exact predicted output quantity

### Out of scope (unless user explicitly expands)

- Router / multi-hop swaps
- LP deposit, withdraw, pool creation
- Generic public EOSIO actions from CLOAK tx

## Code conventions

- All code, logs, comments in **English**
- English-only UI (no i18n)
- First line of every new/modified code file: repo-relative path comment (see `frontend-engineering-partner.mdc`)
- **Hyphens only:** ASCII `-`; never em dash in copy, strings, comments, or rules
- No trivial helper wrappers; inline obvious one-liners
